summary: This appears to be an FBI evidence inventory document listing a seized hard drive containing images from the Epstein investigation. It references multiple evidence item numbers (NYCO23578 through NYCO23592) that likely correspond to digital evidence files.

events.title: FBI Evidence Inventory Recorded
events.description: An FBI-owned hard drive containing images is documented in an evidence inventory, referencing multiple evidence item numbers from the Epstein investigation.

keyFacts: The document is an FBI evidence inventory dated August 21, 2019.
It references a seized FBI-owned Western Digital hard drive (model WD3003FZEX-0024SA0, serial number MiCC13LZR5).
The hard drive contains images associated with multiple evidence item numbers (NYCO23578 through NYCO23592).
The evidence numbers suggest this is part of the New York Epstein investigation (NYCO prefix).
The document appears to be a master copy of evidence inventory records.
